    title: "The USD 1 Trillion Opportunity: Africa's Agribusiness Market and What It Means for Ghana's Youth",
    slug: { _type: 'slug', current: 'trillion-dollar-africa-agribusiness-opportunity' },
    category: 'Articles',
    excerpt: "Africa's food and agriculture market is projected to grow from USD 280 billion in 2023 to USD 1 trillion by 2030. Ghana's own agribusiness sector is valued at USD 3.8 billion by 2028. The opportunity for young Ghanaian agripreneurs is larger than most people realise.",
    author: 'SWK Ghana',
